WEBVTT

00:04:29.966 --> 00:04:31.538
was getting her fix.

00:04:33.061 --> 00:04:36.534
This is what makes heartbreak
so difficult to heal.

00:04:37.417 --> 00:04:39.425
Addicts know they're addicted.

00:04:39.449 --> 00:04:41.559
They know when they're shooting up.

00:04:41.583 --> 00:04:43.480
But heartbroken people do not.

00:04:44.650 --> 00:04:45.823
But you do now.

00:04:46.587 --> 00:04:50.146
And if your heart is broken,
you cannot ignore that.

00:04:50.649 --> 00:04:54.466
You have to recognize that,
as compelling as the urge is,

00:04:54.490 --> 00:04:57.901
with every trip down memory lane,
every text you send,

00:04:57.925 --> 00:05:01.408
every second you spend
stalking your ex on social media,